    </assertion><omtext class="name">
      <CMP> From von Staudt-Clausen representation of Bernoulli numbers: a(n) = Bernoulli(2n) + Sum_{(p-1)|2n} 1/p.</CMP>
    </omtext><omtext class="comment">
      <CMP> The von Staudt-Clausen theorem states that this number is always an integer.</CMP>
    </omtext><omtext class="reference">
